155
00:11:47,000 --> 00:11:47,790
Tidak boleh.

156
00:11:48,280 --> 00:11:49,400
Aku tidak berhadap banyak.

157
00:11:49,960 --> 00:11:52,350
Aku hanya berharap setiap kali
aku berulang tahun,

158
00:11:52,640 --> 00:11:53,760
